metadata.name: Murakka Lale ETH #1
metadata.description:
Date created 05 Nov 2022
High Res image (2295 × 3964 pixels)

Murakka is a kind of collage, handmade artwork consists of three different marbling art pieces (Ebru/Turkish Paper).

Marbling art pieces are created by Ertugrul Incel with traditional Ebru method, using earth dyes and water-based solution, and transferred on chamois paper. Pieces are combined together in a collage work.

Twitter: @ertugrulincel | Web: ertugrulincel.com
